  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "十八世纪的柯尼斯堡有七座桥，连接着两岸和两座小岛。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "市民们爱问：能不能走过每座桥恰好一次，最后回到出发点？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "数学家欧拉把陆地画成点，桥画成线，图论就此诞生。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "euler-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/euler-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "一个顶点连出的边数，我们叫它的度数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "euler-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/euler-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "欧拉发现：除了起点和终点，每次进入一个点都要有一条边再离开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "euler-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/euler-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.6,
      "size": 41616,
      "text": "所以能一笔画走遍每条边并回到原点，全部顶点度数就必须是偶数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "condition",
      "line_id": "cond-1",
      "filename": "condition-cond-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/condition-cond-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.57,
      "size": 41184,
      "text": "如果恰好有两个奇度顶点，就能画出一条欧拉路径，从一个奇点走到另一个。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "condition",
      "line_id": "cond-2",
      "filename": "condition-cond-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/condition-cond-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "柯尼斯堡四块陆地全是奇度，于是七桥问题根本无解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "condition",
      "line_id": "cond-3",
      "filename": "condition-cond-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/condition-cond-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "满足条件时，用 Hierholzer 算法就能真正拼出这条一笔画路线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "hamilton",
      "line_id": "ham-1",
      "filename": "hamilton-ham-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/hamilton-ham-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "换个问题：能不能走遍每个顶点恰好一次再回到起点？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "hamilton",
      "line_id": "ham-2",
      "filename": "hamilton-ham-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/hamilton-ham-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "这叫哈密顿回路，看似相似，却出奇地难。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "hamilton",
      "line_id": "ham-3",
      "filename": "hamilton-ham-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/hamilton-ham-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "欧拉只需数度数，哈密顿至今没有简单判据，只能小图暴力搜索。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "选一个图形，看它属于欧拉回路、欧拉路径还是无法一笔画。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "拖动滑块，粉色高亮会沿着算法找到的路线逐边点亮。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "一笔画看边的度数，全偶成回路，两奇成路径。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-hamilton-path",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-hamilton-path/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "哈密顿走遍顶点，是图论中著名的难题。"
    },
    {
